{"tid":1287102,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「SANA素顏也漂亮」","createTime":"2019-07-05T05:29:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T10:07:40.000Z","uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2eeb1b010271ee83967d887efc86200232878f33","tid":1287102,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4213/4213340.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4213%2F4213340.jpg&h=e1955b65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE於5日早上現身首爾金浦機場準備前往日本參加活動，怎料正常的出國素顏照卻因此成了南韓網民的標靶，其中一則題為「SANA素顏也漂亮」的新聞一直維持在NATE演藝新聞第一名，一看留言卻全都是負面批評，「這不是SANA（사나）是獅子（사자）吧」、「害怕被斷財路吧」、「太醜了」，還有人幸災樂禍表示：「記者真是～哈哈哈，故意挑這種很醜的照片直接衝康她，哈哈哈哈哈。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4213/4213339.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4213%2F4213339.jpg&h=9abb2d87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲南韓網友反應。（圖／翻攝自NATE）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4213/4213338.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4213%2F4213338.jpg&h=56112d19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「SANA素顏也漂亮」登NATE熱新聞第一。（圖／翻攝自NATE）"},{"pid":"0d2494468708f55bc16523e581d1c762dbe924e8","tid":1287102,"uid":138138,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:31:10.000Z","msg":"塊面咁油都叫素顏？"},{"pid":"8e8f0c00b17348c48dd112f713f3da4a74acc589","tid":1287102,"uid":240608,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0d2494468708f55bc16523e581d1c762dbe924e8","tid":1287102,"uid":138138,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:31:10.000Z","msg":"塊面咁油都叫素顏？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:31:49.000Z","msg":"唔係油。保濕黎"},{"pid":"b053f4b1cee2124286351ee23d5d60941f7b835f","tid":1287102,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"8e8f0c00b17348c48dd112f713f3da4a74acc589","tid":1287102,"uid":240608,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"